-- Australia Must Cap Carbon Emissions, Use Market Mechanism, Gillard Says
-- Marion Rae
-- 2010-07-26T21:46:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-26/australia-must-cap-carbon-emissions-use-market-mechanism-gillard-says.html

          
          
             Australia needs to put a cap on
carbon emissions and use a market mechanism as part of long-term
plans to combat climate change, Prime Minister Julia Gillard
told 2GB radio today.  
